# 코드 테스트

class Teamlck {
  constructor (name) {
    this.name = name
  }
  
  hello () {
    console.log(`${this.name}: hello!`)
  }
  
  bye () {
    console.log(`${this.name}: buy..`)
  }
}

let norux = new Teamlck('norux')
let xuron = new Teamlck('xuron')

norux.hello()
xuron.buy()
